26quot%3B%20for%20customers%20and%20override%20the%20system%20by%20adding%20a%20custom%20price%20for%20the%20item.%20The%20feature%20is%20designed%20to%20accommodate%20items%20for%20sale%20in%20a%20store%20but%20which%20don't%20show%20up%20for%20customers%20in%20Instacart's%20catalog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstacart%20forbids%20shoppers%20from%20adding%20gift%20cards%20to%20orders%2C%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20company%20policy%20seen%20by%20BI%20indicates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20impacting%20consumers%20who%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20fraudulent%20charges%20on%20their%20credit%20card%2C%20but%20even%20more%2C%20Instacart%20has%20to%20be%20seeing%20massive%20chargebacks%2C%20yet%20I%20don't%20see%20they%20are%20doing%20anything%20about%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20shopper%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCustomers%20are%20not%20able%20to%20order%20gift%20cards%20through%20the%20Instacart%20platform%20or%20place%20a%20special%20request%20for%20a%20gift%20card%20via%20chat%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Instacart%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstacart%20also%20tells%20shoppers%20not%20to%20purchase%20gift%20cards%20for%20customers%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20deliver%20food%2C%20groceries%2C%20or%20other%20items%20as%20a%20gig%20worker%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-shoppers-customers-getting-hit-by-gift-card-scam-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715420821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663d1db39686a6f37bfe0204%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business