ck.%20Intrigue.%20Fear.%20I%20was%20flooded%20with%20emotions.%20Bennett%2C%20who's%20three%20years%20older%20than%20me%20and%20was%20a%20bit%20further%20along%20in%20the%20balding%20process%2C%20had%20been%20my%20hair%20loss%20mentor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20growing%20number%20of%20men%20who%20traveled%205%2C000%20miles%20to%20Istanbul%2C%20the%20global%20capital%20for%20hair%20transplant%20surgery.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aa.com.tr%2Fen%2Feconomy%2Faround-1m-people-came-to-turkiye-for-hair-transplant-last-year%2F2785522%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAround%25201%2520million%2520people%2520came%2Cthe%2520Turkish%2520Health%2520Tourism%2520Association.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Turkish%20Health%20Tourism%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20about%20one%20million%20people%20traveled%20to%20Turkey%20for%20a%20hair%20transplant%20in%202022%2C%20spending%20about%20%242%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fsi%3DtdVF9YMQ074A36Ux%26v%3DyITGraC8is0%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBalding%20has%20become%20huge%20global%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%20It's%20projected%20to%20be%20worth%20over%20%2411%20billion%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20new%2C%20promising%20pills%20and%20treatments%20hit%20the%20market%2C%20none%20have%20made%20the%20transplant%20redundant.%20If%20anything%2C%20it's%20booming%2C%20and%20Turkey%20has%20built%20a%20reputation%20as%20the%20go-to%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20Bennett's%20luscious%20hair%20poolside%20was%20the%20first%20moment%20I%20seriously%20considered%20joining%20the%20ranks%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20men%20who%20have%20traveled%20to%20what's%20become%20known%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vice.com%2Fen%2Farticle%2Fxgwmnw%2Fhair-loss-transplant-why-turkey%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHairstanbul%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20deep%20pain%20of%20hair%20loss%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20hair%20loss%20started%20in%202015%2C%20at%2024%20years%20old%2C%20when%20I%20noticed%20a%20bald%20spot%20the%20size%20of%20a%20penny%20on%20my%20head%20in%20a%20Snapchat%20video%20my%20friend%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20eight%20years%2C%20my%20balding%20progressed%20and%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1080%2F13548506.2023.2242049%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20many%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20self-esteem%20deteriorated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20less%20attractive%2C%20less%20masculine%2C%20like%20I%20was%20less%20likely%20to%20find%20a%20partner%2C%20and%20as%20though%20I%20was%20aging%20way%20too%20fast.%20Like%20a%20Real%20Housewife%20once%20said%2C%20in%20my%20mind%20I%20only%20had%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bravotv.com%2Fthe-real-housewives-of-new-york-city%2Fseason-8%2Fvideos%2Fthe-rhony-wives-are-back%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20good%20summers%20left%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20the%20two%20leading%20FDA-approved%20drugs%20for%20hair%20loss%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F34159872%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etopical%20minoxidil%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Rogaine)%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F35238144%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAbstract%2Ceffects%2520associated%2520with%2520oral%2520finasteride.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoral%20finasteride%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Propecia).%20I%20also%20tried%20the%20oral%20version%20of%20minoxidil%2C%20a%20blood%20pressure%20drug%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdermatologists-using-blood-pressure-drug-oral-minoxidil-treat-hair-loss-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edermatologists%20have%20been%20using%20off-label%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20curb%20hair%20loss.%20While%20these%20drugs%20helped%20a%20bit%2C%20I%20wasn't%20consistent%20in%20using%20them.%20Over%20time%2C%20my%20hair%20loss%20significantly%20progressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20combing%20over%20my%20hair.%20When%20I%20talked%20to%20my%20mom%20about%20it%2C%20I%20would%20often%20end%20up%20crying.%20I%20avoided%20looking%20at%20security%20cameras%20or%20in%20mirrors%20that%20might%20expose%20the%20bald%20patch%20at%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head.%20At%20my%20lowest%20point%2C%20I'd%20intentionally%20walk%20out%20of%20rooms%20backwards.%20I%20eventually%20started%20on%20an%20antidepressant%20to%20manage%20my%20intrusive%20thoughts%20about%20my%20receding%20hairline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20the%20majority%20of%202023%20asking%20myself%20if%20I'd%20follow%20in%20Bennett's%20footsteps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20filled%20with%20anxiety%20about%20the%2010-hour%20flight%2C%20about%20the%20prospect%20of%20getting%20surgery%20in%20a%20foreign%20country%2C%20about%20the%20operation%20itself%2C%20and%20%E2%80%94%20most%20intensely%20%E2%80%94%20if%20the%20transplant%20would%20leave%20me%20scabby%20and%20botched.%20My%20head%20spun.%20Do%20I%20fly%205%2C000%20miles%20to%20Turkey%20or%20do%20I%20shave%20my%20head%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrities-who-went-bald-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erock%20a%20naked%20dome%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20put%20my%20journalist%20hat%20on%20and%20dug%20into%20the%20research.%20Aside%20from%20some%20negative%20online%20reviews%2C%20Bennett's%20doctor%2C%20Dr.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drserkanaygin.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESerkan%20Aygin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20seemed%20reputable.%20He%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gq.com%2Fstory%2Fhair-transplant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecited%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20prestigious%20publications%20as%20a%20trusted%20expert%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theeuropeanawards.eu%2Fpremiado%2Fdr.-serkan-aygin-european-award-in-medicine-2019-in-hair-transplant-suergery%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe'd%20won%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20award%20for%20innovations%20in%20hair%20transplant%20surgery%2C%20and%20he%20is%20a%20member%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.intsocderm.org%2Fi4a%2Fpages%2Findex.cfm%3Fpageid%3D3279%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20International%20Society%20of%20Dermatology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20organization%20that%20includes%20members%20from%20respected%20universities%20and%20medical%20centers%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20I%20knew%20at%20least%20four%20other%20New%20Yorkers%20within%20walking%20distance%20from%20my%20apartment%20in%20Manhattan%20who%20had%20gone%20to%20Aygin%2C%20including%20my%20Turkish%20barber%2C%20a%20guy%20from%20my%20gym%20who%20runs%20a%20hookah%20shop%20down%20the%20street%2C%20and%20two%20other%20friends%20who%20live%20in%20Hell's%20Kitchen.%20They%20all%20reported%20a%20great%20experience%20and%20had%20good%20results%20to%20show%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20plunge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3ETurkey's%20pursuit%20to%20become%20the%20hair-transplant%20capital%20of%20the%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr.%20Serkan%20Aygin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e5b72f27898f532d666f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Serkan%20Aygin%20has%20been%20performing%20hair%20transplants%20for%2025%20years.%3Cp%3EKenny%20Wassus%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20boarded%20my%20Turkish%20Airlines%20(or%2C%20as%20I%20called%20it%2C%20%26quot%3BHairlines%26quot%3B)%20flight%20in%20December%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20discover%20the%2021-year-old%20from%20New%20Jersey%20to%20my%20left%20and%20his%20older%20cousin%20to%20my%20right%20were%20also%20headed%20for%20hair%20transplants.%20I%20texted%20my%20friend%2C%20filmmaker%20Kenny%20Wassus%2C%20who%20was%20coming%20along%20to%20capture%20my%20experience%2C%20and%20was%20sitting%20a%20row%20over%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20make%20this%20shit%20up!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHair%20transplants%20are%20cheaper%20in%20Turkey%20%E2%80%94%20for%20a%20few%20reasons.%20The%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20cheaper%20and%20wages%20are%20lower.%20Crucially%2C%20the%20Turkish%20health%20ministry%2C%20keen%20to%20draw%20in%20medical%20tourists%20and%20ambitious%20doctors%2C%20offers%20tax%20breaks%20and%20subsidies%20to%20clinics.%20It's%20working%3A%20Since%202019%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trtafrika.com%2Fturkey%2Fturkiye-ranks-among-top-10-health-tourism-destinations-globally-17801009%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealth%20tourism%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20ballooned%20more%20than%2050%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20United%20States%2C%20hair%20transplants%20range%20from%20%2410%2C000%20to%20%2420%2C000.%20Aygin%20charges%20about%20%243%2C500%2C%20to%20be%20paid%20up%20front.%20This%20includes%20a%20consultation%2C%20the%20operation%20itself%2C%20some%20aftercare%2C%20three%20nights%20in%20a%20four-star%20hotel%2C%20and%20transport%20from%20the%20airport%2C%20the%20hotel%2C%20and%20the%20clinic.%20Flights%20from%20New%20York%20set%20you%20back%20another%20%242%2C000.%20It's%20still%20about%20a%20third%20the%20price%20of%20getting%20the%20operation%20done%20on%20US%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Americans%20flocking%20over.%20In%20the%20sleek%20lounge%20area%20of%20Aygin's%20clinic%2C%20I%20found%20dozens%20of%20balding%20men%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20sitting%20nervously%20on%20sofas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAygin%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20influx.%20He%20told%20me%20his%20clinic%20%E2%80%94%2020%20doctors%2C%2080%20technicians%2C%20and%20eight%20anesthesiologists%20%E2%80%94%20performs%20between%2020%20and%2022%20transplants%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tightly-run%20operation%20starts%20with%20tests%20and%20scans.%20On%20the%20first%20day%2C%20a%20nurse%20drew%20my%20blood%20to%20test%20me%20for%20HIV%20and%20hepatitis%20B%20and%20C.%20After%20the%20results%20came%20back%20negative%2C%20I%20was%20put%20in%20a%20spaceship-like%20booth%20for%203D%20imaging%20to%20assess%20my%20hair%20loss.%20They%20showed%20me%20which%20hair%20strands%20were%20healthy%20(pictured%20in%20green)%20and%20which%20were%20dead%20(pictured%20in%20red).%20The%20doctor%20would%20use%20this%20information%20to%20determine%20his%20approach%20for%20my%20transplant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%223D%20imaging%20of%20hair%20follicles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e5779b4abc992e8c84208%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E3D%20imaging%20of%20my%20hair%20follicles%20revealed%20which%20are%20healthy%2C%20and%20which%20are%20damaged.%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Macnaughton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%20was%20the%20consultation%20with%20Aygin%20himself.%20Walking%20in%20the%20room%2C%20he%20exuded%20Central%20Casting%20for%20a%20celebrity%20doctor%20in%20a%20yet-to-be-produced%20reality%20show%20about%20balding%20men.%20He%20was%20charming%2C%20charismatic%2C%20assertive%2C%20and%20eccentric.%20He%20told%20me%20he%20had%20been%20obsessed%20with%20men's%20hair%20since%20he%20was%20a%20child.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20the%20hunters%20of%20beauty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consultation%20was%20quick%20%E2%80%94%20about%2015%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20had%20to%20make%20a%20rapid%20decision%20about%20my%20new%20hairline.%20I%20was%20prepared%20for%20this.%20The%20only%20critique%20my%20references%20had%20of%20Aygin%20was%20that%20he%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Bpushy%26quot%3B%20with%20his%20vision%20for%20their%20hairlines%2C%20and%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bdidn't%20attentively%20listen%26quot%3B%20to%20their%20requests.%20He's%20been%20practicing%20hair%20transplants%20for%20over%2025%20years%2C%20and%20is%20confident%20in%20his%20opinion.%20So%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20go%20into%20this%20meeting%20with%20a%20clear%20sense%20of%20what%20you%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aygin%20drew%20my%20new%20hairline%20onto%20my%20head%20with%20crayon.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e5bb1b4abc992e8c847e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAygin%20drew%20my%20new%20hairline%20onto%20my%20head%20with%20crayon.%3Cp%3EKenny%20Wassus%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20a%20firm%20vision%20for%20my%20new%20hairline.%20All%20I%20said%20was%20I%20wanted%20something%20%26quot%3Bage%20appropriate.%26quot%3B%20Aygin%20took%20a%20makeup%20crayon%20and%20drew%20my%20new%20hairline%2C%20writing%20numbers%20around%20my%20head%20of%20how%20many%20grafts%2C%20or%20follicular%20units%2C%20would%20be%20transplanted%20in%20each%20area.%20When%20he%20finished%20his%20drawing%2C%20he%20put%20a%20mirror%20up%20to%20my%20face%2C%20and%20told%20me%20I%20was%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20love%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20proposed%20that%20they%20transplant%204%2C000%20grafts%20(within%20their%20typical%20range%20of%20between%203%2C500%20and%204%2C400)%2C%20pulling%20from%20my%20%26quot%3Bdonor%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20the%20regions%20of%20my%20body%20where%20I%20was%20still%20growing%20hair.%20In%20this%20case%2C%203%2C400%20of%20the%20grafts%20would%20be%20pulled%20from%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head%20and%20the%20remaining%20600%20would%20be%20pulled%20from%20my%20beard.%20Each%20graft%20equals%20two%20or%20three%20new%20strands%20of%20hair.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20I%20am%20expected%20to%20grow%208%2C300%20new%20strands%20of%20hair%20when%20the%20results%20appear%20%E2%80%93%20between%20six%20months%20and%20a%20year%20from%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%2015-minute%20consultation%20with%20Aygin%20went%20by%20fast.%20I%20had%20to%20make%20a%20rapid%20decision%20about%20my%20hairline.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e5c649686a6f37bfea33b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%2015-minute%20consultation%20with%20Aygin%20was%20quick.%20I%20had%20to%20make%20a%20rapid%20decision%20about%20my%20hairline.%3Cp%3EKenny%20Wassus%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20happy%20enough%20with%20what%20he%20drew%2C%20so%20I%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BLet's%20do%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20nurse%20escorted%20me%20to%20a%20cafeteria%20for%20a%20grilled%20cheese%20sandwich%20followed%20by%20a%20low%20dose%20of%20Xanax%20to%20quell%20my%20nerves.%20I%20was%20surrounded%20by%20about%2010%20other%20men%20%E2%80%94%20some%20nervously%20waiting%20to%20go%20in%20for%20their%20operation%20and%20others%2C%20bandaged%20and%20bloodied%2C%20who%20had%20just%20finished.%20Once%20I'd%20swallowed%20my%20medication%2C%20I%20was%20escorted%20upstairs%20to%20the%20operating%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EInside%20the%20operation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20concerns%20from%20critics%20of%20the%20Turkish%20hair%20transplant%20wave%20is%20that%20doctors%2C%20incentivized%20by%20tax%20breaks%2C%20set%20up%20clinics%20to%20cash%20in%20and%20then%20leave%20the%20work%20to%20technicians%20that%20the%20patients%20have%20never%20met.%20But%20this%20isn't%20always%20the%20case%2C%20and%20wasn't%20the%20case%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Aygin%20only%20came%20into%20the%20room%20for%20a%20quick%20check%20in%2C%20six%20folks%20greeted%20me%20in%20scrubs%20and%20were%20with%20me%20through%20the%20entire%20operation.%20One%20anesthesiologist%20(who%20came%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20room)%2C%20one%20doctor%2C%20and%20four%20technicians.%20I%20confirmed%20with%20Bennett%20and%20my%20other%20friends%20that%20they'd%20had%20the%20same%20lineup%20of%20professionals%20working%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Technician%20inserts%20healthy%20hair%20into%20Spencer's%20skin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e5906b4abc992e8c84473%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20technician%20inserts%20healthy%20hair%20into%20Spencer's%20skin.%3Cp%3EKenny%20Wassus%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beginning%20was%20the%20scariest%20part.%20I%20was%20connected%20to%20an%20IV%2C%20given%20a%20low%20dose%20of%20fentanyl%20for%20pain%20relief%20and%20sedation%2C%20then%20flipped%20onto%20my%20chest.%20My%20head%20looked%20through%20a%20massage%20table-like%20hole%20as%20they%20spent%2030%20minutes%20injecting%20needles%20into%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head%20to%20anesthetize%20me.%20My%20mouth%20was%20so%20dry%20from%20the%20fentanyl%20that%20I%20couldn't%20swallow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20couple%20of%20hours%20were%20dedicated%20to%20extracting%20healthy%20follicles.%20From%20there%2C%20a%20few%20of%20the%20technicians%20worked%20feverishly%20on%20a%20table%20to%20the%20side%20as%20they%20inserted%20my%20hair%20into%20a%20Choi%20Implanter%20pen%20to%20prepare%20them%20for%20insertion%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Brecipient%20area%26quot%3B%20of%20my%20head%20(i.e.%2C%20the%20bald%20part).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20it%20was%20about%20three%20hours%20of%20artwork.%20One%20of%20the%20technicians%20compared%20the%20process%20to%20crocheting%20a%20sweater%20or%20making%20a%20rug.%20Feeding%20hair%20into%20new%20follicles%20is%20arduous%2C%20and%20requires%20dexterity%20and%20endurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22I%20was%20awake%20for%20throughout%20my%208-hour%20hair%20transplant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e5d23f27898f532d66953%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20awake%20for%20throughout%20my%208-hour%20hair%20transplant.%20At%20times%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20in%20a%20drunken%20stupor.%3Cp%3EKenny%20Wassus%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20fifth%20or%20sixth%20hour%20mark%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20in%20a%20drunken%20stupor.%20(They%20avoid%20general%20anesthesia%20because%20they%20are%20flipping%20your%20body%20around%2C%20and%20they%20want%20you%20to%20get%20up%20to%20eat%20a%20sandwich%20and%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom.)%20That's%20when%20they%20started%20the%20painful%20part%3A%20pulling%20from%20my%20beard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20hurts%20because%20the%20skin%20tissue%20is%20so%20much%20softer%20and%20thinner%20than%20the%20back%20of%20the%20head.%20Unless%20you%20called%20for%20a%20translator%20who%20would%20arrive%20within%2010%20minutes%2C%20nobody%20in%20the%20room%20spoke%20English.%20I%20yelped%20about%2015%20times%20to%20which%20the%20woman%20working%20on%20my%20beard%20would%20say%2C%20%26quot%3Banesthesia!%26quot%3B%20and%20someone%20would%20stick%20another%20needle%20into%20my%20beard%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20numb%20me%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsidering%20I%20was%20awake%20for%20the%20eight-hour%20procedure%2C%20it%20really%20wasn't%20so%20bad%2C%20although%20I%20was%20getting%20impatient%20as%20the%20anesthesia%20wore%20off%20in%20the%20last%20hour.%20I%20remember%20them%20telling%20me%20multiple%20times%20that%20there%20were%20%26quot%3B30%20minutes%20left%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20eventually%20yelled%20%26quot%3Byou've%20said%20that%20%3Cem%3Efive%20times%3C%2Fem%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Spencer%20Macnaughton%20during%20a%20hair%20transplant%20in%20Istanbul%20Turkey%2C%20December%202023%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e5661b4abc992e8c840be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpencer%20Macnaughton%20during%20his%20hair%20transplant%20in%20Istanbul%20Turkey%3Cp%3EKenny%20Wassus%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20finally%20announced%20I%20was%20finished%2C%20it%20was%20around%2010%20p.m.%20They%20took%20me%20back%20to%20the%20cafeteria%20to%20drink%20some%20juice%20and%20eat%20a%20chicken%20breast.%20I%20chatted%20with%20a%20guy%20from%20Detroit%20who%20had%20also%20just%20left%20the%20operating%20room.%20I%20felt%20zonked%2C%20emotional%2C%20proud%2C%20and%20accomplished%2C%20and%20he%20did%20too.%20We%20actually%20did%20the%20damn%20thing!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20scalp%20and%20beard%20were%20gooey%20and%20bloody%20and%20I%20had%20to%20sleep%20with%20bandages%20on%20my%20head%20and%20neck.%20But%20there%20wasn't%20much%20pain%20after%20the%20operation.%20I%20took%20another%20Xanax%20when%20I%20got%20to%20my%20hotel%20room%20and%20slept%20like%20a%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EI'll%20probably%20be%20on%20hair-growth%20drugs%20for%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20hair%20transplant%20isn't%20the%20be-all%20and%20end-all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20post-operation%20laser%20therapy%20that%20Aygin%20said%20would%20speed%20up%20my%20recovery.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e59a0b4abc992e8c84559%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20post-operation%20laser%20therapy%20that%20Aygin%20said%20would%20speed%20up%20my%20recovery.%3Cp%3EKenny%20Wassus%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAygin%20recommends%20that%20I%20continue%20taking%20minoxidil%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20finasteride%20because%20they%20reduce%20the%20production%20of%20DHT%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmy.clevelandclinic.org%2Fhealth%2Farticles%2F24555-dht-dihydrotestosterone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehormone%20associated%20with%20hair%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20men.%20He%20says%20it's%20important%20to%20take%20these%20drugs%20not%20to%20maintain%20the%20transplanted%20hair%2C%20since%20these%20follicles%20were%20taken%20from%20my%20donor%20area%20where%20I'm%20not%20expected%20to%20experience%20hair%20loss%2C%20but%20rather%20to%20keep%20the%20vulnerable%20hair%20I%20had%20before%20the%20transplant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20these%20two%20drugs%20costs%20upwards%20of%20%2460%20a%20month%20and%20can%20be%20sourced%20by%20companies%20like%20Keeps%2C%20Hims%2C%20Roman%20and%20other%20businesses%20that%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyITGraC8is0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrying%20to%20capitalize%3C%2Fa%3E%20off%20of%20changing%20male%20beauty%20standards.%20It's%20a%20huge%20investment.%20Sitting%20in%20Istanbul%2C%20having%20gone%20all-in%20on%20hair%20retention%2C%20I%20felt%20compelled%20to%20follow%20his%20advice.%20Time%20will%20tell%20if%20I%20stick%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short-term%2C%20there%20were%20some%20dos%20and%20don'ts%20for%20the%20healing%20process.%20No%20sex%20or%20alcohol%20for%20five%20days%2C%20no%20cardio%20for%20two%20weeks%2C%20no%20weight%20lifting%20for%20three%20weeks%2C%20and%20no%20sauna%20or%20steam%20room%20for%20two%20months.%20You%20need%20to%20sleep%20on%20your%20back%20and%20with%20an%20airplane%20pillow%20behind%20your%20head%20for%20the%20first%20seven%20days%20(this%20was%20not%20fun).%20You%20also%20need%20to%20wear%20a%20hat%20outside%20during%20daylight%20at%20all%20times%20for%20the%20first%20two%20months.%20And%20you%20need%20to%20abide%20by%20a%20rigorous%20shampoo%20and%20lotion%20regimen%20for%20the%20first%20month.%20A%20technician%20also%20performed%20a%20low-level%20laser%20procedure%2024%20hours%20after%20the%20operation%2C%20which%20they%20said%20would%20speed%20up%20my%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20the%20operation%2C%20Kenny%20and%20I%20were%20driven%20to%20the%20Istanbul%20Airport%2C%20where%20literally%20every%20fourth%20man's%20head%20was%20raw%20from%20a%20transplant.%20I%20spoke%20to%20around%2015%20of%20them.%20Business%20executives%2C%20a%20waiter%2C%20a%20lawyer%2C%20and%20a%20real%20estate%20agent.%20They%20were%20all%20giddy%20%E2%80%94%20proud%20of%20themselves%20and%20glad%20they%20took%20the%20leap%20of%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3ESomehow%2C%20a%20cosmetic%20treatment%20lifted%20me%20in%20a%20way%20I%20never%20expected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20now%20been%20about%20four%20months%20since%20the%20operation.%20The%20recovery%20has%20been%20a%20breeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Men%20at%20Istanbul%20Airport%20post-hair%20transplant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e5959b4abc992e8c844f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20Istanbul%20Airport%2C%20with%20my%20fellow%20hair%20transplanters.%3Cp%3EKenny%20Wassus%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20about%206-7%20months%20to%20see%20serious%20results%20and%20about%20a%20year%20for%20final%20results.%20But%20over%20the%20last%20month%2C%20I've%20noticed%20new%20strands%20of%20hair%20populating%20my%20hairline%20every%20day.%20I%20now%20want%20to%20pose%20for%20pictures%20with%20my%20friends%20and%20family.%20I%20feel%20more%20confident%20in%20Zoom%20and%20in-person%20work%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAesthetics%20aside%2C%20knowing%20I%20took%20control%20of%20something%20that%20at%20one%20point%20was%20shattering%20my%20self%20esteem%20has%20lifted%20me%20in%20a%20way%20I%20didn't%20think%20possible.%20Even%20if%20the%20transplant%20doesn't%20continue%20to%20work%20or%20one%20day%20falls%20out%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20happy%20and%20proud%20that%20I%20gave%20it%20a%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20do%20it%20again%2C%20and%20I%20just%20might%20need%20to.%20Aygin%20told%20me%20before%20I%20booked%20my%20flight%20that%20I'd%20need%20two%20operations%20to%20get%20full%20coverage.%20This%20first%20procedure%20should%20fully%20restore%20my%20hairline%2C%20but%20I'll%20still%20have%20a%20bald%20spot%20on%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head.%20My%20barber%20and%20Bennett%20have%20already%20gone%20back%20for%20their%20second%20treatments%2C%20and%20are%20happy%20with%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20me%2C%20I'm%20elated.%20And%2C%20who%20knows%E2%80%A6%20maybe%20this%20summer%20it'll%20be%20Bennett%2C%20my%20friend%20who%20inspired%20this%20whole%20journey%2C%20who%20falls%20over%20when%20he%20sees%20my%20new%20hairline%20at%20the%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhair-transplant-istanbul-turkey-personal-experience-business-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715420761000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e5d80f27898f532d669e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhair-transplant-istanbul-turkey-personal-experience-business-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Spencer%20Macnaughton%20started%20noticing%20his%20hairline%20receding%20at%2024%20years%20old.%20He%20tried%20everything%20to%20retain%20it.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20millions%20of%20men%20flocking%20to%20Turkey%20for%20a%20hair%20transplant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Spencer%20Macnaughton)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhair-transplant-istanbul-turkey-personal-experience-business-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Billionaires%20like%20Jeff%20Bezos%20and%20Steve%20Jobs%20are%20spending%20six%20figures%20a%20year%20maintaining%20their%20superyachts.%20Here's%20why.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3