E%3Cp%3EA%20superyacht%2C%20generally%20over%2030%20meters%20long%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20assets%20money%20can%20buy%2C%20with%C2%A0the%20largest%20costing%20more%20than%20a%20lot%20of%20real%20estate%20or%20a%20private%20jet.%20Billionaires%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-yachts-owned-by-tech-billionaires-mark-zuckerberg-jeff-bezos-2024-5%23laurene-powell-jobs-venus-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeff%20Bezos%2C%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20and%20Steve%20Jobs%20each%20spent%20nine%20figures%20on%20their%20megayachts.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20include%20operating%20costs.%20Owners%20should%20expect%20to%20pay%20about%2010%25%20of%20a%20yacht's%20new-build%20price%20each%20year%2C%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20That's%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20annually%20for%20the%20most%20luxurious%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20small-to-medium-sized%20business%20in%20its%20own%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jeffrey%20Beneville%2C%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20at%20insurance%20company%20NFP%2C%20where%20he%20specializes%20in%20consulting%20clients%20about%20yachts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emany%20smaller%20boats%2C%20superyachts%20need%20staff%2C%20not%20just%20a%20captain.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuperyacht-etiquette-how-to-behave-on-yacht-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuperyachts%20have%20space%20for%20dozens%20of%20crewmembers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20a%20chef%2C%20engineer%2C%20and%20masseuse%20for%20the%20guests%20onboard.%20Each%20gets%20an%20annual%20salary%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest-ranking%20members%20earn%20six%20figures%20%E2%80%94%20and%20benefits.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-schmidt-superyacht-whisper-kismet-bought-jaguars-billionaire-shahid-khan-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEric%20Schmidt's%20yacht%3C%2Fa%3E%20fits%20a%20crew%20of%2028%20for%20a%20ratio%20of%20about%20two%20crewmembers%20per%20guest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20fuel%2C%20dockage%20fees%2C%20routine%20maintenance%2C%20and%20insurance.%20The%20latter%20hinges%20on%20everything%20from%20the%20reputation%20of%20a%20yacht's%20shipyard%20to%20where%20an%20owner%20wants%20to%20take%20it%20(if%20a%20vessel%20is%20taking%20frequent%20trips%20to%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20for%20example%2C%20expect%20to%20pay%20a%20higher%20premium).%20If%20a%20superyacht%20has%20a%20support%20yacht%20%E2%80%94%20or%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-yacht-superyacht-koru-beautiful-amazing-insiders-say-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20superyacht%2C%20in%20Bezos%3C%2Fa%3E'%20case%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0expect%20to%20pay%20another%2010%25%20of%20that%20boat's%20price%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cost%20to%20maintain%20a%20yacht%C2%A0is%20so%20high%20that%20they%20just%20think%20that%20money's%20getting%20lit%20on%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthew%20Fleissig%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20wealth%20management%20firm%20Pathstone%2C%20told%20BI%20of%20his%20clients%20who%20choose%20to%20charter%20rather%20than%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20firm's%20clients%20who%20%3Cem%3Edoes%3C%2Fem%3E%20own%20has%20a%2023-meter%20yacht%20valued%20at%20%245.2%20million.%20The%20annual%20cost%20to%20staff%2C%20maintain%2C%20dock%2C%20and%20insure%20the%20boat%20is%20%24346%2C297%2C%20according%20to%20documentation%20provided%20to%20BI.%20The%20lion's%20share%20is%20spent%20on%20marina%20fees%20(%2495%2C970)%20and%20maintenance%20work%20(%2488%2C408.)%20While%20not%20exactly%20a%20Sunfish%2C%20that%20boat%20is%20too%20small%20to%20count%20as%20a%20superyacht.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20106%20meters%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-oligarchs-megayacht-costs-taxpayers-nearly-1-million-a-month-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_bl