0struggling%20to%20find%20skilled%20labor%20amid%20a%20national%20shortage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20construction%20industry%20is%20short%20about%20500%2C000%20workers%20due%20to%20limits%20on%20immigration%20and%20disinvestment%20in%20trade%20schools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20high%20wages%2C%20stigma%20around%20the%20building%20trades%20and%20more%20flexible%20job%20alternatives%20are%20deterring%20new%20workers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Michael%20Bodei%20went%20into%20construction%2031%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20was%20a%20faster%20way%20to%20make%20the%20kind%20of%20salary%20he%20wanted%20than%20becoming%20a%20lawyer%2C%20the%20other%20career%20option%20he%20was%20weighing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBodei's%20family%20has%20been%20in%20the%20construction%20business%20for%20generations%2C%20so%20he'd%20seen%20how%20lucrative%20it%20could%20be%20to%20build%20and%20renovate%20upscale%20single-family%20homes%20in%20affluent%20suburbs.%20At%2022%2C%20Bodei%20started%20his%20own%20general%20and%20building%20contracting%20company%2C%20Bodei%20Contracting%2C%20in%20Morristown%2C%20New%20Jersey.%20By%2025%2C%20he'd%20done%20well%20enough%20to%20buy%20a%20lake%20house%2C%20a%20boat%2C%20a%20new%20Corvette%2C%20a%20motorcycle%2C%20and%20two%20trucks%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20because%20I%20was%20a%20genius%2C%20it%20was%20because%20it%20was%20that%20easy%20to%20get%20into%20my%20business%20and%20be%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20Bodei%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BHouses%20were%20cheaper%2C%20everything%20was%20more%20abundant.%20It%20was%20just%20an%20easier%20place%20in%20time%20to%20do%20business%20than%20it%20is%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20keys%20to%20his%20success%3A%20%26quot%3Bmore%20skilled%20less%20expensive%20labor%2C%26quot%3B%20Bodei%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20his%20employees%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20core%20group%20of%20about%20a%20dozen%20people%20that%20expands%20to%20around%2030%20in%20busy%20times%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0have%20worked%20for%20the%20company%20for%20decades.%20Their%20projects%20are%20largely%20six-figure%20kitchen%20and%20bathroom%20renovations%20and%20additions%20on%20%242%20million%20to%20%245%20million%20homes.%20And%20because%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20this%20high-end%20work%2C%20Bodei%20generally%20doesn't%20hire%20anyone%20without%20at%20least%2010%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20a%20national%20shortage%20of%20construction%20workers%2C%20it's%20become%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20find%20new%20workers%2C%20from%20electricians%20and%20plumbers%20to%20those%20with%20specialty%20skills%20in%20fiberglass%20work%20and%20cabinetry%2C%20Bodei%20said.%20A%20pipeline%20of%20younger%20skilled%20workers%20just%20isn't%20there.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20one%20to%20replace%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20He%20worries%20that%20as%20older%20workers%20retire%2C%20their%20skills%20will%20be%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20unusual%20for%20anybody%20under%2040%20to%20be%20working%20for%20us%2C%20people%20under%2050%20are%20unusual%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20our%20carpenters%20is%20in%20his%2070s.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20housing%20is%20in%20large%20part%20a%20result%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aeaweb.org%2Farticles%3Fid%3D10.1257%2Fjep.32.1.3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erestrictive%20zoning%20laws%20and%20building%20regulations%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20construction%20worker%20shortage%20is%20also%20pushing%20up%20home%20costs.%20Fewer%20construction%20workers%20means%20less%20%E2%80%94%20and%20slower%20%E2%80%94%20residential%20construction%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haas.berkeley.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FHoward_Wang_Zhang_Housing-Supply-and-Construction-Labor-Dayin-Zhang.pdf%3Fref%3Dthebuildersdaily.com%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWe%2520show%2