2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20construction%20industry%20is%20short%20about%20500%2C000%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20%26quot%3Bon%20top%20of%20the%20normal%20pace%20of%20hiring%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.org%2FNews-Media%2FNews-Releases%2Fabc-2024-construction-workforce-shortage-tops-half-a-million%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20January%202024%20news%20release%20from%20the%20trade%20group%20Associated%20Builders%20and%20Contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20issue%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F03%2F21%2Fbusiness%2Fconstruction-industry-needs-immigrant-workers%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elimits%20on%20immigration%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20a%20perhaps%20more%20structural%20cause%20is%20the%20gradual%20disinvestment%20in%20technical%20and%20trade%20schools%20in%20favor%20of%20colleges%20and%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20get%20more%20people%20interested%20in%20construction%20as%20a%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20Ken%20Simonson%2C%20chief%20economist%20at%20the%20Associated%20General%20Contractors%20of%20America%2C%20recently%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Adding%20that%20everyone%20from%20the%20federal%20government%20to%20school%20guidance%20counselors%20needs%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20the%20message%20to%20kids%20that%20there%20are%20lucrative%20rewarding%20%E2%80%94%20both%20financially%20and%20in%20satisfaction%20%E2%80%94%20careers%20in%20construction.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20to%20college%20to%20have%20a%20good%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWages%20are%20quite%20high%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20especially%20for%20skilled%20tradespeople.%20Most%20of%20Bodei's%20employees%20make%20at%20least%20%24100%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20he%20said.%20But%20construction%20has%20lost%20some%20of%20its%20edge%20as%20compensation%20in%20other%20industries%2C%20including%20restaurants%20and%20hospitality%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstateline.org%2F2024%2F01%2F09%2Fhospitality-workers-wages-are-rising-faster-than-high-earners-in-most-states%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20risen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20remote%20and%20hybrid%20jobs%20offer%20cushier%2C%20more%20flexible%20alternatives%2C%20Simonson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20there's%20long%20been%20a%20widespread%20stigma%20around%20working%20in%20the%20building%20trades%2C%20despite%20the%20relatively%20high%20salaries%20they%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20I%20was%20in%20school%2C%20you%20were%20discouraged%20from%20going%20because%20that%20was%20where%20the%20stupid%20kids%20went%2C%20which%20is%20hilarious%20because%20you%20could%20go%20make%20six%20figures%20as%20a%20plumber%20in%20your%20mid-20s%2C%26quot%3B%20Bodei%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBodei%20would%20be%20worried%20about%20the%20future%20of%20construction%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20be%20his%20problem%20for%20much%20longer.%20He's%20planning%20to%20close%20his%20business%20next%20year%20and%20relocate%20to%20South%20Florida%2C%20where%20he%20also%20has%20real%20estate%20investments%20%E2%80%94%20and%20easy%20access%20to%20the%20beach.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20gonna%20go%20relax%20for%20a%20while%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20figure%20out%20what%20my%20next%20thing%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomebuilder-no-one-to-replace-retiring-boomer-construction-workers-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715420221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663bea8ef27898f532d542f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomebuilder-no-one-to-replace-retiring-boomer-construction-workers-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There's%20a%20growing%20shortage%20of%20skilled%20construction%20workers%2C%20and%20long-time%20contractor%20Michael%20Bodei%20says%20it's%20made%20business%20much%20more%20challenging.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Eliza%20Relman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhomebuilder-no-one-to-replace-retiring-boomer-construction-workers-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226-Year-Old's%20Body%20Left%20Behind%2C%20Pak%20Flight%20Takes%20Off%20With%20Grieving%20Parents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20deeply%20distressing%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20the%20staffers%20of%20a%20Pakistan%20International%20Airlines%20(PIA)%20flight%20bound%20for%20Skardu%20from%20Islamabad%20forgot%20to%20put%20the%20body%20of%20a%20six-year-old%20boy%20on%20the%20fight%20while%20his%20grieving%20parents%20embarked%20on%20their%20journey%2C%20unaware%20that%20their%20beloved%20son's%20body%20was%20left%20behind%2C%20Dawn%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%2C%20overwhelmed%20by%20shock%20and%20disbelief%2C%20fainted%20upon%20learning%20that%20their%20son's%20remains%20had%20been%20inadvertently%20left%20behind%20at%20Islamabad's%20airport%2C%20a%20realisation%20that%20struck%20with%20devastating%20force%20upon%20their%20arrival%20at%20Skardu%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMujtaba%2C%20a%20young%20resident%20of%20Katshi%20village%20in%20the%20Kharmang%20district%2C%20had%20been%20battling%20a%20grave%20illness--a%20tumour--requiring%20medical%20attention%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20his%20hometown.%20Initially%20diagnosed%20in%20Skardu%2C%20he%20was%20subsequently%20referred%20to%20Rawalpindi%20for%20treatment%2C%20where%20he%20remained%20under%20the%20care%20of%20physicians%20at%20Benazir%20Bhutto%20Hospital%20for%20several%20weeks.%20Tragically%2C%20Mujtaba%20succumbed%20to%20his%20ailment%20on%20Thursday%2C%20leaving%20his%20grieving%20parents%20to%20navigate%20the%20painful%20process%20of%20arranging%20for%20his%20final%20journey%20home%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20intent%20to%20transport%20their%20beloved%20son's%20body%20to%20their%20native%20village%20of%20Katshi%20for%20burial%2C%20Mujtaba's%20parents%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20PIA%20flight%20departing%20from%20Islamabad%20on%20Friday.%20Recognising%20the%20impracticality%20of%20a%20gruelling%2024-hour%20road%20journey%20in%20the%20sweltering%20heat%2C%20they%20opted%20for%20air%20travel%2C%20hoping%20to%20expedite%20their%20return%20to%20their%20community%20to%20bid%20their%20final%20farewells%20to%20their%20cherished%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20should%20have%20been%20a%20solemn%20and%20respectful%20journey%20turned%20into%20a%20nightmare%20of%20unimaginable%20proportions.%20Despite%20diligently%20adhering%20to%20all%20requisite%20procedures%20and%20regulations%2C%20the%20grief-stricken%20parents%20arrived%20at%20Islamabad%20airport%20at%20the%20crack%20of%20dawn%2C%20meticulously%20completing%20the%20cargo%20formalities%20for%20their%20son's%20remains%20in%20accordance%20with%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20and%20the%20airline's%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ibrahim%20Asadi%2C%20a%20relative%20of%20the%20boy%2C%20the%20family's%20scheduled%20departure%20time%20of%209%20am%20was%20marred%20by%20an%20unforeseen%20delay%2C%20prolonging%20their%20departure%20until%201%20pm.%20Little%20did%20they%20know%20that%20amidst%20this%20delay%2C%20a%20grave%20error%20had%20occurred--one%20that%20would%20shatter%20their%20already%20fragile%20world%20upon%20their%20arrival%20in%20Skardu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20clock%20struck%202%20pm%20at%20Skardu%20airport%2C%20the%20stark%20reality%20of%20the%20situation%20came%20crashing%20down%20upon%20Mujtaba's%20parents.%20In%20a%20cruel%20twist%20of%20fate%2C%20they%20were%20informed%20that%20their%20son's%20body%20had%20been%20left%20behind%20in%20Islamabad--a%20revelation%20that%20plunged%20them%20into%20a%20state%20of%20utter%20disbelief%20and%20despair.%20Tears%20flowed%20freely%20as%20the%20parents%20grappled%20with%20the%20magnitude%20of%20their%20loss%2C%20while%20their%20anguished%20cries%20echoed%20through%20the%20airport%20lounge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFueled%20by%20grief%20and%20righteous%20indignation%2C%20the%20relatives%20of%20the%20boy%20swiftly%20mobilised%2C%20uniting%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20flagrant%20negligence%20displayed%20by%20the%20airline%20management.%20Their%20voices%20rang%20out%20in%20unified%20condemnation%2C%20demanding%20accountability%20and%20justice%20for%20the%20unforgivable%20oversight%20that%20had%20robbed%20them%20of%20the%20opportunity%20to%20bid%20a%20proper%20farewell%20to%20their%20beloved%20son%20and%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20chaos%2C%20officials%20from%20PIA%2C%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authority%2C%20and%20other%20pertinent%20agencies%20scrambled%20to%20placate%20the%20aggrieved%20family%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20gravity%20of%20their%20error%20and%20vowing%20to%20rectify%20the%20situation%20without%20delay.%20Assurances%20were%20made%2C%20promises%20of%20swift%20action%20and%20restitution%20offered%2C%20yet%20the%20wounds%20inflicted%20upon%20Mujtaba's%20family%20remained%20raw%20and%20unhealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20tumult%2C%20Yousaf%20Kamal%2C%20another%20grieving%20relative%2C%20levelled%20damning%20accusations%20against%20the%20airline%2C%20suggesting%20a%20deliberate%20act%20of%20negligence.%20Allegations%20surfaced%20regarding%20the%20flight's%20delayed%20departure%2C%20purportedly%20to%20accommodate%20the%20travel%20plans%20of%20a%20federal%20minister%2C%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Mujtaba's%20remains%20languishing%20at%20Islamabad%20airport%2C%20Dawn%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715420160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-