ay%20(UBT%20Chief)%20and%20other%20opposition%20leaders%20will%20all%20be%20in%20jail.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20granted%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20interim%20bail%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Questioning%20the%20arrest%20just%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20court%20directed%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20to%20investigate%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20after%20voting%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20one-and-a-half%20years%20he%20was%20there...%20he%20could%20have%20been%20arrested%20before%20or%20after%20(the%20election)%20also.%20Whatever%20it%20is%2C%2021%20days%20here%20or%20there%20should%20not%20make%20any%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20release%20has%20been%20cheered%20by%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20is%20a%20key%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715419200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F1j4dmcak_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_11_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-2-months-yogi-adityanath-will-arvind-kejriwal-big-claim-if-bjp-wins-5638967%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20addressing%20his%20first%20press%20conference%20since%20leaving%20jail%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20will%20not%20only%20imprison%20Opposition%20leaders%20but%20also%20leaders%20from%20their%20own%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-2-months-yogi-adityanath-will-arvind-kejriwal-big-claim-if-bjp-wins-5638967%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-2-months-yogi-adityanath-will-arvind-kejriwal-big-claim-if-bjp-wins-5638967%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv