20crowned%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMr.%20England%2C%20Mr.%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Mr.%20Britain%2C%20and%20Mr.%20World.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20can't%20discredit%20Taylor's%20dedication%20to%20training%20and%20nutrition%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20his%20later-in-life%20success%20comes%20down%20to%20potatoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20shock%20those%20who%20have%20been%20led%20to%20believe%20that%20carbs%20are%20the%20enemy%20of%20fat%20loss.%20The%20anti-carb%20movement%20has%20been%20around%20in%20various%20guises%20for%20decades.%20The%20low-carb%20Atkins%20diet%20was%20popular%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20the%20high-fat%2C%20low-carb%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-ways-keto-ruined-my-relationship-with-food-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eketo%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20gained%20traction%20in%20the%202000s%2C%20and%20now%20there%20is%20increasing%20fear-mongering%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-weight-loss-12-pounds-spiking-increasing-blood-sugar-levels-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblood%20sugar%20%26quot%3Bspikes%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20caused%20by%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20eating%20carbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20Taylor%20found%2C%20carbs%20are%20an%20important%20part%20of%20our%20diets%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-carbs-not-better-than-brown-health-weight-loss-dietitians-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earen't%20inherently%20fattening%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20muscle%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Taylor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e39afb4abc992e8c804f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Taylor%20(center)%20competing%20in%20Mr%20Universe.%3Cp%3EMark%20Taylor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204adb260-974c-476e-ae3b-06b12a10399d%5C%22%3ECarbs%20help%20replenish%20energy%20stores%20in%20our%20muscles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20denying%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-protein-maximize-muscle-gains-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotein%20is%20important%20for%20muscle%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20protein%20contains%20amino%20acids%2C%20which%20are%20the%20building%20blocks%20of%20muscle.%20But%20carbs%20are%20important%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarbs%20provide%20the%20body%20with%20energy%20that%20is%20stored%20in%20the%20muscles%20as%20glycogen.%20When%20we%20exercise%2C%20we%20deplete%20these%20glycogen%20stores%2C%20so%20eating%20carbs%20after%20working%20out%20replenishes%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20have%20more%20energy%2C%20you%20can%20also%20train%20harder%2C%20indirectly%20helping%20you%20build%20more%20muscle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20eating%20right%20(in%20the%20right%20quantity)%2C%20to%20build%20muscle%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eyou%20need%20to%20train%20hard%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprogressive-overload-fitness-meaning-and-how-to-do-it-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprogressive%20overload%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ensure%20you're%20resting%20enough%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20focusing%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaked-oats-recipes-high-protein-breakfast-ideas-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarbs%20that%20release%20energy%20slowly%3C%2Fa%3E%20(in%20Taylor's%20case%2C%20sweet%20potatoes%20and%20oats)%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20maintain%20relatively%20stable%20energy%20levels%20throughout%20the%20day.%20Eating%20white%20potatoes%2C%20which%20release%20energy%20faster%2C%20after%20training%2C%20however%2C%20helps%20replenish%20glycogen%20stores%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221548b140-b1e0-4ceb-9fe8-83136ca49474%5C%22%3ETaylor%20started%20bodybuilding%20at%20a%20young%20age%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20teenager%2C%20Taylor%20had%20a%20job%20lifting%20crates%20of%20drinks%20on%20and%20off%20lorries%2C%20and%20he%20started%20growing%20some%20muscle%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20saw%20the%20cover%20of%20a%20men's%20fitness%20magazine%20in%20a%20shop%20around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20mind%20trying%20to%20be%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%20So%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2019%2C%20he%20started%20going%20to%20the%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gym%20owner%2C%20a%20bodybuilder%2C%20spotted%20Taylor's%20potential%20and%20invited%20the%20young%20man%20to%20train%20with%20him.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20Taylor%20entered%20his%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fachieving-dream-working-bodybuilder-man-lost-over-hundred-pounds-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebodybuilding%20competition%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20finished%20second%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst-timers%26quot%3B%20category.%20The%20year%20after%20that%2C%20he%20won%20the%20overall%20Scottish%20championship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20start%20of%20Taylor's%20decadeslong%20bodybuilding%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20on%20to%20win%20a%20few%20Scottish%20titles%2C%20but%20I%20was%20never%20really%20good%20enough%2C%20and%20by%20the%20time%20I%20was%20going%20to%20the%20British%20finals%2C%20I%20was%20just%20getting%20blown%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%2C%20now%2052%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20felt%20I%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20go%20in%20and%20win%20all%20the%20things%2C%20but%20I%20just%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20get%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-facts-arnold-schwarzenegger-fitness-diet-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMr.%20Universe%3C%2Fa%3E%20felt%20too%20unrealistic%20to%20even%20be%20a%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed54de5b-2848-4ef8-b3f9-f11d58dce22c%5C%22%3ETaylor%20changed%20his%20diet%2010%20years%20ago%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20ate%20a%20strictly%20high-protein%2C%20low-carb%20diet%20when%20preparing%20for%20competitions%20because%20that's%20what%20he%20saw%20other%20bodybuilders%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20average%20day%2C%20Taylor%20might%20have%20eaten%20some%20oats%20at%20breakfast%20and%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20rice%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20but%20he%20said%20his%20diet%20mostly%20focused%20on%20chicken%20and%20broccoli.%20That's%20despite%20his%20intense%20training%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20getting%20any%20carbohydrates%20for%20energy%2C%20so%20I%20just%20constantly%20went%20about%20feeling%20not%20very%20good%2C%20feeling%20ill%2C%20and%20my%20training%20wasn't%20very%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20until%2C%20in%202014%2C%20a%20nutritionist%20and%20coach%20called%20Vicky%20McCann%20who'd%20seen%20Taylor%20competing%2C%20offered%20to%20help%20him%20with%20his%20nutrition%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20send%20her%20his%20food%20diary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20just%20looked%20at%20it%20and%20ripped%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCann%20gave%20him%20a%20new%20diet%20plan%20which%20consisted%20of%2010%20meals%20a%20day%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feat-carbs-more-food-to-lose-fat-better-energy-nutritionist-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarbohydrates%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20when%20I%20transformed%20my%20physique%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor's%20muscle%20mass%20grew%20like%20never%20before.%20Within%20a%20year%2C%20he%20finished%20second%20in%20Britain%20in%20a%20bodybuilding%20contest%2C%20before%20reaching%20the%20over-45s%20divisions%20and%20winning%20his%20string%20of%20titles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b462