raining-data-source-solutions-openai-meta-google-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escrambling%20for%20AI%20training%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20seems%20to%20have%20one%20big%20advantage%20over%20its%20rivals%3A%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20Chris%20Cox%2C%20told%20Bloomberg's%20Tech%20Summit%20on%20Thursday%20that%20it%20uses%20publicly%20available%20photos%20and%20text%20from%20the%20platforms%20to%20train%20its%20text-to-image%20generator%20model%20called%20Emu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20train%20on%20private%20stuff%2C%20we%20don't%20train%20on%20stuff%20that%20people%20share%20with%20their%20friends%2C%20we%20do%20train%20on%20things%20that%20are%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20text-to-image%20model%20can%20produce%20%26quot%3Breally%20amazing%20quality%20images%26quot%3B%20because%20Instagram%20has%20many%20photos%20of%20%26quot%3Bart%2C%20fashion%2C%20culture%20and%20also%20just%20images%20of%20people%20and%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Cox%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20can%20create%20images%20on%20Meta%20AI%20by%20typing%20a%20prompt%20starting%20with%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bimagine%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20will%20generate%20four%20images%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20models%20need%20to%20be%20fed%20and%20trained%20on%20data%20for%20them%20to%20be%20effective.%20It's%20been%20a%20contentious%20issue%20as%20there's%20almost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-leverage-harry-potter-test-putting-value-data-ai-models-2023-