g%20the%20boys%20wearing%20the%20acne%20treatment%20mask.%20As%20per%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20they%20took%20a%20selfie%20with%20the%20mask%20on%20their%20faces%20during%20a%20sleepover%20in%202017%2C%20apparently%20in%20solidarity%20with%20a%20friend%20suffering%20from%20severe%20acne.%20The%20treatment%2C%20bought%20by%20one%20of%20the%20boys'%20mothers%2C%20was%20light%20green%20when%20applied%20and%20turned%20dark%20green%20once%20dry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20selfie%2C%20which%20the%20boys%20said%20was%20a%20joke%20and%20not%20a%20racial%20insult%2C%20went%20viral%20in%202020%20and%20many%20labelled%20it%20as%20depicting%20blackface.%20However%2C%20on%20Monday%2C%20a%20Santa%20Clara%20County%20jury%20sided%20with%20the%20boys'%20claims%20that%20the%20school%20breached%20oral%20contract%20and%20had%20a%20lack%20of%20due%20process%20in%20forcing%20them%20out.%20The%20jury%20awarded%20the%20money%20and%20tuition%20reimbursement%20to%20the%20two%20former%20students%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F05%2F09%2Fus-news%2Fteens-kicked-out-of-luxe-catholic-school-for-blackface-awarded-1m%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPost%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20case%20is%20significant%20not%20only%20for%20our%20clients%20but%20for%20its%20groundbreaking%20effect%20on%20all%20private%20high%20schools%20in%20California%2C%20which%20are%20now%20legally%20required%20to%20provide%20fair%20procedure%20to%20students%20before%20punishing%20or%20expelling%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Krista%20Baughman%2C%20one%20of%20the%20attorneys%20for%20the%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20jury%20rightly%20confirmed%20that%20Saint%20Francis%20High%20School's%20procedures%20were%20unfair%20to%20our%20clients%20and%20that%20the%20school%20is%20not%20above%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Baughman%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F