s%2C%20We%20Will...%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress%20Chief's%20Big%20Promise%20For%20'Make%20In%20India'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20today%20said%20that%20his%20party%20resolves%20to%20make%20the%20country%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%20by%20raising%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20from%2014%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20GDP%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriting%20about%20making%20(manufacturing)%20in%20India%20on%20his%20official%20X%20handle%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20resolves%20to%20make%20India%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%20by%20raising%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20from%2014%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20GDP%20in%20the%20next%205%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELauding%20the%20Congress's%20regime%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20claimed%20that%20the%20nation's%20manufacturing%20share%20of%20GDP%20was%20higher%20compared%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20thus%20no%20surprise%20that%20in%20the%20last%2025%20years%2C%20India's%20manufacturing%20share%20of%20GDP%20has%20been%20higher%20during%20the%20Congress%20rule.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20(2014-24)%2C%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20has%20stagnated%20at%20just%2014%25%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20also%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20is%20determined%20to%20make%20India%20the%20manufacturing%20powerhouse%20that%20produces%20goods%20and%20services%20for%20itself%20and%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20also%20said%20that%20the%20party's%20immediate%20objective%20will%20be%20to%20restore%20a%20healthy%2C%20fearless%20and%20trustworthy%20climate%20for%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20party's%20goal%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%201991%20abolished%20industrial%20licensing%20and%20controls.%20%26quot%3BThe%20independent%20regulatory%20regime%20that%20was%20put%20in%20place%20has%20deteriorated%20into%20a%20system%20of%20overt%20and%20covert%20controls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20conduct%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20of%20the%20current%20rules%20and%20regulations%20and%20repeal%20or%20amend%20them%20in%20order%20to%20restore%20freedom%20to%20industry%2C%20business%20and%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20Congress'%20ambition%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20party%20will%20aim%20for%20India%20to%20attain%20a%20position%20of%20leadership%20in%20multiple%20industries%20such%20as%20steel%2C%20metals%2C%20garments%20and%20textiles%2C%20cement%2C%20automobiles%2C%20electronic%20goods%2C%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20engineering%20goods%2C%20petroleum%20products%2C%20chemicals%2C%20and%20mining%20rare%20earth%20and%20critical%20minerals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutting%20forward%20RBI's%20data%20on%20stalled%20projects%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20that%20Congress%20will%20revive%20those%20projects%20by%20taking%20the%20help%20of%20the%20private%20sector.%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20RBI%2C%20nearly%2060%25%20of%20the%20large%20central%20government%20projects%20have%20been%20stalled%20or%20delayed%20and%20costs%20have%20risen%20by%20nearly%205%20lakh%20crores.%20Congress%20will%20address%20the%20problem%20in%20a%20mission%20mode%20and%20find%20ways%20and%20means%20to%20revive%20the%20stalled%20projects%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20private%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrowing%20light%20on%20the%20Congress%20approach%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20will%20reform%20the%20production%20linked%20incentives%20(PLI)%20scheme%20to%20target%20specific%20sectors%20that%20can%20create%20thousands%20of%20jobs%20by%20making%20India%20one%20of%20the%20top%205%20producers%20in%20the%20world%20in%20that%20sector.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20also%20mentioned%20about%20introducing%20an%20employment-linked%20incentive%20scheme.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20introduce%20a%20new%20employment-linked%20incentive%20(ELI)%20Scheme%20for%20corporates%20to%20win%20tax%20credits%20for%20additional%20hiring%20against%20regular%2C%20quality%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20the%20party's%20opposition%20to%20monopolies%20and%20oligopolies%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20will%20create%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20all%20businesses.%20We%20are%20opposed%20to%20monopolies%20and%20oligopolies.%20We%20will%20strengthen%20the%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%20(CCI)%20to%20ensure%20that%20India%20will%20be%20an%20open%20and%20competitive%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20President%20also%20talked%20about%20strengthening%20AI%20and%20robotics%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20encourage%20and%20support%20the%20use%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20robotics%2C%20etc.%20which%20will%20create%20new%20and%20frontline%20jobs.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20will%20ensure%20that%20there%20are%20more%20job%20opportunities%20in%20sectors%20that%20use%20conventional%20technology.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715406480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F10bq500g_mallikarjun-kharge-pm-narendra-modi_625x300_01_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-5-years-we-will-congress-chiefs-big-promise-for-make-in-india-5637934%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20today%20said%20that%20his%20party%20resolves%20to%20make%20the%20country%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%20by%20raising%20the%20