ne%20to%20prevent%20minors%20seeing%20harmful%20content.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Ftechnology-68994263%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20Indian-American%20Billionaire's%20Dinner%20For%20Biden%2C%20POTUS%20Talks%20Of%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EProminent%20Indian-American%20billionaire%20and%20venture%20capitalist%20Vinod%20Khosla%20hosted%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20at%20his%20Silicon%20Valley%20residence%20for%20an%20election%20fundraiser%20during%20which%20the%20Democratic%20Party's%20presumptive%20candidate%20raised%20more%20than%20USD%201.5%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETickets%20for%20the%20fundraiser%20on%20Friday%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20Mr%20Khosla%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Sun%20Microsystems%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Khosla%20Ventures%2C%20ranged%20from%20USD%206%2C600%20to%20USD%20100%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20election%20cycle%2C%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20president%20attended%20a%20fundraiser%20hosted%20by%20an%20Indian-American.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20USD%201.5%20million%20was%20raised%20during%20the%20event%20attended%20by%20many%20Indian-Americans%20from%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20area.%20There%20were%20about%2050%20people%20seated%20and%2030%20or%20so%20standing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%2C%20which%20lasted%20for%20about%2015%20minutes%2C%20President%20Biden%20focused%20more%20on%20immigration%20and%20women's%20rights.%20He%20also%20spoke%20about%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20did%20say%20that%20the%20US%20is%20not%20a%20xenophobic%20country%2C%20Biden%20did%20not%20mention%20India%20and%20Japan%20this%20time%20unlike%20his%20controversial%20remarks%20at%20a%20fundraiser%20in%20Washington%20DC%20about%20a%20week%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(immigrants)%20have%20been%20incredible%20contributors%20to%20the%20work%20ethic%20of%20this%20country%20--%20incredible.%20One%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20we%20continue%20to%20grow%20is%20we%20are%20not%20xenophobic.%20We%20have%20the%20input%20of%20new%20immigrants%20coming%20into%20the%20country%20that%20should%20come%20into%20the%20country%20that%20are%20generating%20economic%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20amidst%20applause%20from%20the%20select%20group%20of%20fundraisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20was%20introduced%20at%20the%20fundraiser%20by%20Mr%20Khosla%2C%20the%20host.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVinod%20and%20Neeru%20(Khosla)%2C%20thank%20you.%20Thank%20you%20for%20that%20introduction%20and%20your%20whole%20family.%20You%20know%2C%20one%20of%20the%20bad%20news%20about%20being%20a%20child%20or%20a%20nephew%20in%20a%20deeply%20involved%20family%20is%20you%20have%20no%20way%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20for%20inviting%20us%20to%20your%20wonderful%20home%20because%20I%20came%20to%20see%20your%20dogs.%20As%20the%20press%20can%20tell%20you%2C%20I%20like%20dogs%20better%20than%20people%20sometimes%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Biden%2C%2081%2C%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20love%20and%20affection%20towards%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident's%20speech%20writer%20Vinay%20Reddy%20was%20among%20senior%20White%20House%20officials%20who%20accompanied%20Biden%20to%20the%20fundraiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20way%20to%20the%20Khosla%20residence%2C%20the%20presidential%20convoy%20was%20greeted%20by%20both%20Israeli%20and%20pro-Palestinian%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%20stood%20with%20an%20Israeli%20flag%20and%20a%20sign%20that%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%20Biden''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20mile%20away%2C%20a%20group%20of%20about%20two%20dozen%20protesters%20were%20at%20an%20intersection%20with%20signs%20that%20read%20%26quot%3BHands%20off%20Rafah%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCease%20fire%20now%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20four%20people%20waved%20US%20and%20Israeli%20flags%20as%20the%20motorcade%20took%20the%20final%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%2C%20President%20Biden%20made%20several%20jokes%20about%20the%20former%20president%20and%20his%20Republican%20Party%20rival%20Donald%20Trump.%20%26quot%3BNot%20everyone%20is%20feeling%20the%20enthusiasm%20these%20days.%20The%20other%20day%20this%20guy%20walked%20up%2C%20said%20I'm%20in%20real%20trouble%2C%20short%20on%20cash%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20I%20said%20Donald%20I%20can't%20help%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20a%20slight%20twist%20from%20a%20line%20about%20bleach%20in%20Trump's%20hair%20and%20instead%20said%20he%20should%20have%20injected%20it%3A%20%26quot%3BRemember%20him%20saying%20the%20best%20thing%20to%20do%20is%20to%20inject%20a%20little%20bleach%20into%20your%20arm%E2%80%A6%20I%20wish%20he%20had%20done%20it%20a%20little%20bit%20himself.%26quot%3B%20He%20talked%20about%20Trump's%20pride%20in%20%26quot%3Blove%20letters%20from%20South%20Korean%20president%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%2C%26quot%3B%20presumably%20meaning%20North%20Korean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20urged%20the%20audience%20to%20read%20Trump's%20interview%20with%20Time%20magazine.%20He%20talked%20about%20reports%20that%20Trump%20asked%20oil%20executives%20to%20donate%20USD%201%20billion%20to%20his%20campaign%2C%20doing%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20cross.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20Bhutoria%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20National%20Finance%20Committee%20of%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Committee%2C%20who%20also%20attended%20the%20fundraiser%2C%20said%20Indian-Americans%20could%20sway%20the%20outcome%20in%20several%20battleground%20states%2C%20potentially%20affecting%20the%20November%205%2C%202024%20race%20for%20the%20White%20House%20in%20support%20of%20President%20Biden%20and%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhutoria%2C%20who%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20Joe%20Biden's%20campaign%20since%20its%20inception%2C%20underscored%20the%20pivotal%20role%20of%20Asian%20Americans%2C%20particularly%20South%20Asian%20and%20Indian%20Americans%2C%20in%20what%20he%20considers%20one%20of%20the%20most%20critical%20elections%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Federal%20Election%20Commission%20records%2C%20Khosla%20has%20so%20far%20given%20approximately%20USD%201.4%20million%20to%20Democratic%20campaigns%20and%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20prominent%20venture%20capitalist%2C%20he%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Sun%20Microsystems.%20He's%20known%20for%20his%20investments%20in%20technology%20startups%20and%20advocacy%20for%20clean%20technology%20and%20renewable%20energy.%20Khosla%20Ventures%2C%20his%20venture%20capital%20firm%2C%20has%20funded%20numerous%20successful%20companies%20in%20various%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khosla%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20political%20advocacy%2C%20particularly%20in%20issues%20related%20to%20technology%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20the%20environment.%20While%20he%20has%20contributed%20to%20political%20causes%20and%20candidates%2C%20his%20political%20support%20and%20involvement%20may%20vary%20over%20time%20and%20depend%20on%20the%20specific%20issues%20and%20candidates%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20is%20set%20to%20face%20former%20President%20Trump%20in%20the%20November%205%2C%202024%2C%20presidential%20election%2C%20a%20rematch%20between%20them%20since%20their%202020%20clash.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715404920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F644p31c4_biden-fundraiser-hosted-by-vinod-khosla_625x300_11_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fat-indian-am