g%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EProspective%20homeowners%20who%20haven't%20started%20construction%20should%20also%20invest%20in%20an%20underground%20sump%20for%20harvesting%20rainwater.%20There%20is%20no%20silver%20bullet%20to%20solve%20water%20crises%20entirely.%20This%20will%20afford%20you%20more%20than%20a%20decent%20level%20of%20self-sufficiency.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7hk2trq1Pf%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7hk2trq1Pf%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20rohitmalekar.eth%20(%40RohitMalekar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRohitMalekar%2Fstatus%2F1769432478224175571%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20their%20neighbours%20rely%20on%20drying%20borewells%2C%20Suma%20and%20Rohit%20opted%20for%20roof-based%20rainwater%20harvesting%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20their%202%2C000%20sq%20ft%20home%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%EF%BF%BDWe%20learnt%20that%20even%20borewells%20as%20deep%20as%201%2C000%20feet%20in%20our%20locality%20went%20dry%20over%20time.%20This%20was%20the%20reason%20we%20chose%20not%20to%20drill%20a%20borewell.%20Besides%2C%20we%20still%20depend%20on%20water%20tankers%20as%20the%20Cauvery%20water%20supply%20is%20insufficient.%20This%20dependency%20increases%20during%20summer%20with%20the%20Cauvery%20water%20supply%20reducing%20to%20one-fourth%20of%20its%20usual%20quantity%2C%EF%BF%BD%20Rohit%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20harvest%20rainwater%20for%20non-potable%20purposes%20like%20cleaning%2C%20bathing%2C%20and%20gardening%20needs%2C%20except%20for%20drinking%20and%20cooking.%20This%20ensures%20they%20are%20unaffected%20by%20the%20depleting%20groundwater%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERainwater%20meets%20half%20of%20the%20family%EF%BF%BDs%20annual%20water%20needs.%20%EF%BF%BDEvery%20monsoon%2C%20we%20save%20up%20to%2035