2visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349093%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20IMD%20warnings%20about%20heatwaves%20in%20several%20cities%2C%20here%20are%20few%20things%20that%20they%20can%20learn%20from%20Ahmedabad's%20Heat%20Action%20Plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349093%2Fahmedabad-heat-action-plan-summer-heatwave-2024-lessons-tips-model-blueprint%2F%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20appeared%20first%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98We%E2%80%99re%2079%20%26amp%3B%20We%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Stop%E2%80%99%3A%20Couple%20Uses%20Boats%20to%20Bring%20Healthcare%20to%20Remote%20Indian%20Islands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20Dr%20Anowarul%20Alam%20is%20finishing%20up%20dressing%20a%20patient%EF%BF%BDs%20wound%2C%20his%20phone%20buzzes.%20Anyone%20privy%20to%20the%20conversation%20would%20know%20that%20it%20is%20another%20patient%20on%20the%20line.%20She%20is%20running%20a%20fever%20and%20needs%20antibiotics%20urgently.%20Calling%20Dr%20Alam%20is%20one%20of%20her%20options%3B%20the%20other%20is%20a%20three-day%20walk%20from%20the%20remote%20island%20in%20the%20Sundarbans%20where%20she%20lives%20to%20the%20nearest%20Government%20hospital.%20It%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20which%20one%20she%20chooses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20her%20out%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20Dr%20Alam%20shouts%20out%20instructions%20to%20someone%3A%20%EF%BF%BDWe%20need%20to%20move%20fast.%EF%BF%BD%20A%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20roaring%20of%20an%20engine%20is%20indicative%20of%20a%20boat%20preparing%20to%20head%20to%20its%20next%20destination.%20As%20the%20white%20vessel%20powers%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F305137%2Fneelanjan-chakravarty-from-kolkata-builds-homestay-in-sunderbans-west-bengal-travel-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaters%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%3C%2Fa%3E%20(one%20of%20the%20largest%20mangrove%20forests%20in%20the%20world%20located%20in%20West%20Bengal)%2C%20the%20team%20inside%20%EF%BF%BD%20the%20doctor%2C%20a%20nurse%2C%20an%20x-ray%20technician%2C%20a%20lab%20technician%2C%20a%20pharmacist%20%EF%BF%BD%20busy%20themselves%20keeping%20medicines%20and%20equipment%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20unique%20concept%2C%20%EF%BF%BDIn%20a%20month%2C%20we%20treat%2034%2C578%20patients%20in%20total%2C%EF%BF%BD%20Dr%20Alam%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20shying%20away%20from%20taking%20credit%20for%20this%20massive%20volume.%20%EF%BF%BDThere%20are%20four%20boats%20in%20total%20and%20the%20schedule%20for%20each%20is%20set%20every%20Monday.%20Throughout%20the%20week%2C%20we%20travel%20across%20the%2030%20islands%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%2C%20covering%20six%20blocks%20in%20the%20North%20and%2013%20in%20the%20South.%20On%20Sundays%2C%20we%20return%20to%20the%20mainland%20where%20we%20stock%20up%20on%20supplies%2C%20medicines%2C%20rest%20and%20recharge%20for%20the%20next%20week.%EF%BF%BD%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Alam%20has%20been%20doing%20this%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20doctors%20to%20be%20appointed%20by%20the%20couple%20Mohammed%20Abdul%20Wohab%20and%20Sabitri%20Pal%20%EF%BF%BD%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20SHIS%20Foundation%20(Southern%20Health%20Improvement%20Samity)%20started%20in%201980%20%EF%BF%BD%20when%20Wohab%2C%20a%20lawyer%2C%20and%20Pal%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20bonded%20over%20their%20intentions%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F278313%2Fsundarbans-hingalganj-island-english-medium-schoo